54 static void* AppleGLGetProcAddress (const char* name)
55 {
56 static bool initialized = false;
57 static void * handle = NULL;
58 if (!handle)
59 {
60 if (!initialized)
61 {
62 initialized = true;
63 const char * const path = "/System/Library/Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/Versions/Current/OpenGL";
64
65 handle = dlopen(path, RTLD_LAZY | RTLD_GLOBAL);
66 }
67 if (!handle)
68 return NULL;
69 }
70 return dlsym(handle, name);
71 }
72 #endif // __APPLE__
73
74 #if defined(__sgi) || defined (__sun)
75 #include <dlfcn.h>
76 #include <stdio.h>
77
78 static void* SunGetProcAddress (const char* name)
79 {
80 typedef void* (func_t*)(const GLubyte*);
81
82 static void* h = 0;
83 static func_t gpa = 0;
84
85 if (!h)
86 {
87 h = dlopen(NULL, RTLD_LAZY | RTLD_LOCAL);
88 if (!h)
89 return 0;
90 gpa = (func_t) dlsym(h, "glXGetProcAddress");
91 }
92
93 return gpa ? gpa((const GLubyte*) name) : dlsym(h, name);
94 }
95 #endif // __sgi || __sun
96
97 #if defined(_WIN32)
98 #ifdef _MSC_VER
99 #pragma warning(disable: 4055)
100 #pragma warning(disable: 4054)
101 #endif
102
103 static int TestPointer(const PROC pTest)
104 {
105 if(!pTest)
106 return 0;
107
108 ptrdiff_t iTest = (ptrdiff_t) pTest;
109
110 if (iTest == 1 || iTest == 2 || iTest == 3 || iTest == -1)
111 return 0;
112
113 return 1;
114 }
115
116 static PROC WinGetProcAddress(const char* name)
117 {
118 PROC pFunc = wglGetProcAddress((LPCSTR) name);
119 if (TestPointer(pFunc))
120 return pFunc;
121
122 HMODULE glMod = GetModuleHandleA("OpenGL32.dll");
123 return (PROC) GetProcAddress(glMod, (LPCSTR) name);
124 }
125 #endif // _WIN32
126
127 #if defined(_WIN32)
128 #define CV_GL_GET_PROC_ADDRESS(name) WinGetProcAddress(name)
129 #elif defined(__APPLE__)
130 #define CV_GL_GET_PROC_ADDRESS(name) AppleGLGetProcAddress(name)
131 #elif defined(__sgi) || defined(__sun)
132 #define CV_GL_GET_PROC_ADDRESS(name) SunGetProcAddress(name)
133 #else // GLX
134 #include <GL/glx.h>
135
136 #define CV_GL_GET_PROC_ADDRESS(name) glXGetProcAddressARB((const GLubyte*) name)
137 #endif
138
139 static void* IntGetProcAddress(const char* name)
140 {
141 void* func = (void*) CV_GL_GET_PROC_ADDRESS(name);
142 if (!func)
143 {
144 std::ostringstream msg;
145 msg << "Can't load OpenGL extension [" << name << "]";
146 CV_Error(CV_OpenGlApiCallError, msg.str());
147 }
148 return func;
149 }
150#else
151 static void* IntGetProcAddress(const char*)
152 {
153 CV_Error(CV_OpenGlNotSupported, "The library is compiled without OpenGL support");
154 return 0;
155 }
156#endif
